channel.title: Anyone that has a red x in the corner of your screen look at this
channel.description:
ok... everyone who has that stupid x in the top of their moparscape screen here is wut you do..... go to google.com... then type moparscape download..... click the first link..... then click on the first here you see..... after that wait 10 seconds and on the bottom right of your screen click download.... after it finishes downloading it should then be a window on your desktop.....
hope i helped someone!!!!! have fun!!!
